---
title: Beef Meatballs & Mumbai Tomato Sauce with Brown Rice & Herby Yoghurt
description: Beef meatballs become super scrumptious when coated in a tomato based sauce, mildly spiced and all on top of a helping of
brown rice, tossed through with salad leaves. A cooling yoghurt soothes everything and brings this delicious dish to perfection.

